### Restaurant Order System - API Tests
### Verwende die VS Code Extension "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ─── Health Check ───────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ─── Menü ───────────────────────────────────

### Komplette Speisekarte
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu

### Kategorien
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/categories

### Menü durchsuchen
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/search?q=Schnitzel

### ─── Tische ─────────────────────────────────

### Alle Tische
GET {{baseUrl}}/tables

### ─── Bestellungen ───────────────────────────

### Neue Bestellung (Küche)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "target": "kitchen",
  "waiter_name": "Max",
  "notes": "Tisch am Fenster",
  "items": [
    { "menu_item_id": 8, "quantity": 2, "unit_price": 22.90, "notes": "medium" },
    { "menu_item_id": 12, "quantity": 1, "unit_price": 13.90 }
  ]
}

### Neue Bestellung (Bar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "target": "bar",
  "waiter_name": "Max",
  "items": [
    { "menu_item_id": 36, "quantity": 2, "unit_price": 4.80 },
    { "menu_item_id": 43, "quantity": 1, "unit_price": 8.50 }
  ]
}

### Aktive Bestellungen
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### Küchen-Bestellungen
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/kitchen

### Bar-Bestellungen
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/bar

### Status ändern (ersetze :id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "in_progress" }

### Bestellung fertig
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "ready" }

### Tagesstatistiken
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/today/stats
